    {
      "title": "Tout va bien",
      "context": [
        "This group project, conducted in the second year of engineering school between two promotions, was on a free theme. We chose to focus on helping school students in academic difficulty, through an autonomous questionnaire capable of identifying their needs and offering them adapted resources.",
        "For my part, I took care of the entire visual identity: creation of the logo, development of the graphic charter, and design of wireframes and interactive prototypes on Figma, putting a real focus on accessibility and user experience. We also conducted semi-structured interviews with experts, using user-centered design methods to expand our knowledge and verify the consistency of our model for the selected need.  I also had the opportunity to pass on my knowledge about Figma to the first years of the group, which was a super enriching experience.",
        "My school assigning projects with free themes like this is really cool, as it allows us to explore topics that speak to us and also helps us become more responsible."
      ],
      "created": "2024-12-19",
      "duration": "4",
      "projectDuty": ["UX/UI Design"],
